\c 46
\s UJakobe uya eGibithe
\p
\v 1 UIsrayeli wasesuka lakho konke ayelakho, wafika eBerisheba\x + 21.31,33; 26.23,33; 28.10.\x*, wanikela imihlatshelo kuNkulunkulu kayise uIsaka\x + 26.24,25.\x*.
\v 2 UNkulunkulu wasekhuluma kuIsrayeli emibonweni\x + 15.1.\x* yebusuku esithi: Jakobe, Jakobe! Wasesithi: Khangela, ngi\add lapha\add*.
\v 3 Wasesithi: NginguNkulunkulu, uNkulunkulu kayihlo\x + 28.13.\x*; ungesabi ukwehlela eGibithe, ngoba ngizakumisa ube yisizwe esikhulu khona\x + 12.2. Dute. 26.5.\x*;
\v 4 mina ngizakwehlela eGibithe lawe, njalo lami isibili ngizakwenyusa\x + 15.16; 28.15; 48.21; 50.24. Eks. 3.8.\x*; futhi uJosefa uzabeka isandla sakhe phezu kwamehlo akho\x + 50.1.\x*.
\v 5 UJakobe wasesukuma evela eBerisheba. Lamadodana kaIsrayeli amthwala uJakobe uyise labantwanyana bawo labomkawo ezinqoleni uFaro ayezithumile ukumthwala\x + 45.19,21,27.\x*.
\v 6 Basebethatha izifuyo zabo lempahla zabo ababezizuzile elizweni leKhanani, bafika eGibithe, uJakobe lenzalo yakhe yonke laye,
\v 7 amadodana akhe, lamadodana amadodana akhe kanye laye, lamadodakazi akhe, lamadodakazi amadodana akhe; layo yonke inzalo yakhe wayiletha laye eGibithe\x + 37.35. Josh. 24.4. Hlab. 105.23. Isa. 52.4.\x*.
\s Inzalo kaJakobe
\p
\v 8 Njalo la ngamabizo amadodana kaIsrayeli\x + Eks. 6.14-25. Eks. 1.1-5.\x* afika eGibithe: UJakobe lamadodana akhe. Izibulo likaJakobe: URubeni\x + Nani 26.5-7. 1 Lan. 5.1-3.\x*.
\v 9 Lamadodana kaRubeni: OHanoki, loPalu, loHezironi, loKarimi.
\p
\v 10 Lamadodana kaSimeyoni: OJemuweli loJamini loOhadi loJakini loZohari, loShawuli indodana yomKhananikazi.
\p
\v 11 Lamadodana kaLevi\x + 1 Lan. 6.1.\x*: OGerishoni, uKohathi loMerari.
\p
\v 12 Lamadodana kaJuda\x + 1 Lan. 2.3; 4.21.\x*: OEri loOnani loShela loPerezi loZera; kodwa uEri wafa, loOnani, elizweni leKhanani\x + 1 Lan. 2.3; 4.21.\x*. Lamadodana kaPerezi ayengoHezironi loHamuli\x + e 38.29. 1 Lan. 2.5.\x*.
\p
\v 13 Lamadodana kaIsakari\x + 1 Lan. 7.1.\x*: OThola loPuva loYobi loShimroni.
\p
\v 14 Lamadodana kaZebuluni: OSeredi loEloni loJaleli.
\v 15 La ngamadodana kaLeya awazalela uJakobe ePadani-Arama loDina indodakazi yakhe\x + 29.32-30.21.\x*; yonke imiphefumulo yamadodana akhe lamadodakazi akhe yayingamatshumi amathathu lantathu.
\p
\v 16 Amadodana kaGadi-ke: UZifiyoni loHagi, uShuni loEziboni, uEriyi loArodi loAreli\x + Nani 26.15-17.\x*.
\p
\v 17 Lamadodana kaAsheri\x + 1 Lan. 7.30.\x*: OJimna loIshiva loIshivi loBeriya loSera udadewabo. Lamadodana kaBeriya: OHeberi loMalikiyeli.
\v 18 La ngamadodana kaZilipa\x + 30.10-13.\x*, uLabani amnika yena uLeya indodakazi yakhe\x + 29.24.\x*, njalo la wawazalela uJakobe, imiphefumulo elitshumi lesithupha.
\p
\v 19 Amadodana kaRasheli umkaJakobe: OJosefa loBenjamini.
\p
\v 20 Kwasekuzalelwa uJosefa elizweni leGibithe oManase loEfrayimi, amzalela bona uAsenathi indodakazi kaPotifera umpristi\f + \fk umpristi: \fl kumbe, \fq induna.\f* weOni\x + 41.50.\x*.
\p
\v 21 Lamadodana kaBenjamini: OBhela loBekeri loAshibeli, uGera loNamani, uEhi loRoshi, uMupimi loHupimi loAridi\x + Nani 26.38-40. 1 Lan. 7.6-12; 8.1.\x*.
\v 22 La ngamadodana kaRasheli azalelwa uJakobe; yonke imiphefumulo ilitshumi lane.
\p
\v 23 Lamadodana kaDani: UHushimi.
\p
\v 24 Lamadodana kaNafithali\x + 1 Lan. 7.13.\x*: OJazeli loGuni loJezeri loShilema.
\v 25 La ngamadodana kaBiliha\x + 30.5-8.\x*, uLabani amnika yena uRasheli indodakazi yakhe\x + 29.29.\x*, wasemzalela la uJakobe; yonke imiphefumulo iyisikhombisa.
\p
\v 26 Yonke imiphefumulo eyafika loJakobe eGibithe, evela ekhalweni lwakhe, ngaphandle kwabafazi bamadodana kaJakobe, yonke imiphefumulo ingamatshumi ayisithupha lesithupha\x + Eks. 1.5. Dute. 10.22. Seb. 7.14.\x*.
\v 27 Lamadodana kaJosefa awazalelwa eGibithe ayimiphefumulo emibili. Yonke imiphefumulo yendlu kaJakobe eyafika eGibithe yayingamatshumi ayisikhombisa.
\s UJakobe labantwana bakhe eGibithe
\p
\v 28 Wasethuma uJuda phambi kwakhe kuJosefa, ukuthi akhokhele phambi kwakhe esiya eGosheni; basebefika elizweni leGosheni\x + 45.10.\x*.
\v 29 UJosefa wasebopha inqola yakhe, wenyukela eGosheni ukuhlangabeza uIsrayeli uyise; wazibonakalisa kuye, wawela entanyeni yakhe, wakhala inyembezi isikhathi eside entanyeni yakhe\x + 45.14.\x*.
\v 30 UIsrayeli wasesithi kuJosefa: Sengingafa, lokhu sengibonile ubuso bakho, ngoba usaphila.
\v 31 UJosefa wasesithi kubafowabo lakundlu kayise: Ngizakwenyuka ngibike kuFaro ngithi kuye: Abafowethu lendlu kababa ababeselizweni leKhanani sebefikile kimi\x + 47.1.\x*;
\v 32 lamadoda angabelusi bezimvu, ngoba abengamadoda afuyileyo; njalo alethe izimvu zawo lenkomo zawo lakho konke alakho.
\v 33 Njalo kuzakuthi lapho uFaro elibiza esithi: Iyini imisebenzi yenu\x + 47.3.\x*?
\v 34 Lizakuthi-ke: Inceku zakho zingamadoda okufuya\x + 46.32.\x*, kusukela ebutsheni bethu kuze kube khathesi\x + 37.12.\x*, thina sonke labobaba; ukuze lihlale elizweni leGosheni; ngoba wonke umelusi wezimvu uyanengeka kumaGibithe\x + 43.32. Eks. 8.26.\x*.
